dcterms:creator: A. Khalil
J. Kwon
dcterms:description: A dataset collected by a human driver navigating a training track using the OSCAR simulator, capturing visual observations and critical control values such as steering angle, throttle position, braking pressure, time, velocity, acceleration, and position.
dcterms:title: D (Training Dataset)

dcterms:creator: A. Khalil
J. Kwon
dcterms:description: A dataset generated from the original dataset D, mapping input observations to distinct future actions corresponding to different latency values for training the Timed Action Prediction Model (TAPM).
dcterms:title: DTAPM (Dataset for Timed Action Prediction Model)

dcterms:creator: J. Kwon
dcterms:description: An open-source robotic car architecture simulator designed for research and education, providing a customizable environment for testing autonomous vehicle algorithms.
dcterms:title: OSCAR Simulator
